{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-jsx","path":"/projects/risotto-play/","result":{"data":{"post":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/2adcb/risotto-play.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'313\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M23%2016l-1%20266c1%202%202%202%205%202l6%202a7021%207021%200%2000341-2h4V151l-1-135c-2-2-352-2-354%200m164%206c-4%201-2%204%203%204l4-1h13c11%200%2013%200%2013-2l-1-1h-3c-1-1-2-1-3%201h-3l-5-1h-6l-2%201h-2l-1-1h-7\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/ba381/risotto-play.webp 200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/7f61c/risotto-play.webp 400w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/d00b9/risotto-play.webp 800w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/92f8c/risotto-play.webp 1200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/fad48/risotto-play.webp 1600w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/90d15/risotto-play.webp 1984w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/772e8/risotto-play.png 200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/e17e5/risotto-play.png 400w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/5a190/risotto-play.png 800w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/c1b63/risotto-play.png 1200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/29007/risotto-play.png 1600w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/2adcb/risotto-play.png 1984w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/5a190/risotto-play.png\"\n          alt=\"Risotto Play\"\n          title=\"Risotto Play\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sometime back in 2018, a friend of mine started building his own programming language, <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://github.com/risotto/risotto\" title=\"\"Risotto\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">\"Risotto\"</a> (although I wanted the name to be \"Ravioli\" so the syntax could be <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9r8Swai8_g&feature=youtu.be&t=32\" title=\"\"Ravioli Ravioli, give me the formuoli\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">\"Ravioli Ravioli, give me the formuoli\"</a>, but I digress).</p>\n<p>Anywho, I've enjoyed using services such as <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://goplay.space/\" title=\"The Go Play Space\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">The Go Play Space</a> and <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://repl.it/\" title=\"Repl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Repl</a> in the past, and wanted to replicate this kind of environment (whilst paying 0 for hosting) for Risotto.</p>\n<h2><a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://api.play.risotto.dev\" title=\"The API\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">The API</a></h2>\n<p>This runs on <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://kubesail.com/\" title=\"Kubesail\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Kubesail</a> for easy K8s deployment (and the free tier), with the API written in Go, and spawning a process running the code passed to it.</p>\n<p>In order to keep the API service performant, there's a little bit of IP addressed rate limiting, and runtime constraints, but overall the traffic is low enough that this hasn't come close to being an issue yet.</p>\n<p>The API is designed so that if anyone wants, they can use it for their own purposes, which is highly encouraged (get Risotto out there!)</p>\n<p>It is also covered with Unit Tests, and automatic CI/CD.</p>\n<h2><a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://play.risotto.dev\" title=\"The UI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">The UI</a></h2>\n<p>This is hosted with <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://pages.github.com/\" title=\"GitHub pages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">GitHub pages</a> for easy CI/CD and just fantastic performance.</p>\n<p>Written in React (TypeScript flavour), it's fairly simple but is optimised for responsive design and even has a cute little \"Share\" feature, so you can share your creations with others.</p>","excerpt":"Sometime back in 2018, a friend of mine started building his own programming language,  (although I wanted the name to be \"Ravioli\" so the syntax could be , but I digress). Anywho, I've enjoyed using…","frontmatter":{"title":"🍲 Risotto Play","date":"April, 2020","tech":["Go","TypeScript","React"],"link":"https://play.risotto.dev/","source":"https://github.com/risotto/play-ui","previewImage":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/f3583/risotto-play.png","height":940,"width":1200}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/risotto-play/"}}}